        </article>

        <article class="subsection">
            <h3>2.3) Permissions and Security</h3>
            <table class="component-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>Role</th>
                    <th>Access</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Administrator</td>
                    <td>Full access to all adjustments</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Inventory Manager</td>
                    <td>Can create, edit, and delete</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Warehouse Staff</td>
                    <td>Adjustment creation only</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Restricted User</td>
                    <td>No access or read-only (depending on configuration)</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </article>
    </section>

    <!-- Conclusion -->
    <section class="conclusion">
        <h2>Conclusion</h2>
        <p>
            With Movelys' stock adjustment module, companies have a reliable, structured, and secure tool to <strong>maintain inventory accuracy in all circumstances.</strong> This system not only allows quick error correction but also helps analyze root causes to implement lasting corrective actions.
        </p>
        <p>
            By providing complete visibility on stock modifications and facilitating internal controls, Movelys transforms stock adjustments into a true <strong>lever for quality control and logistical optimization.</strong> It's an indispensable solution for any organization looking to improve stock management reliability, limit losses, and ensure the integrity of commercial data.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>